• Approach
  • About us
Developed by a team of programmers and ML–enthusiasts
the tool for AI/ML projects concentrated on team work and rapid development

Hide target for test set. Without exceptions

We want to help teams to organize work by implementing the best practices of teamwork in one place. So you don’t have to keep them in your mind.

We think that existing products do not instill the right habits in terms of teamwork and do not bring the proper tradeoff speed/reliability of the result.

See your teammate work in realtime

Team Leaderboard
This interface allows you to&nbsp;check metrics for all submitted solutions on&nbsp;current task, search for best/worst metric values, make fast text search for submits, hide some fields, etc. Moreover, breadcrumbs on&nbsp;top of&nbsp;the window allows you to&nbsp;switch to&nbsp;all available in&nbsp;GUI tasks and check out scores on&nbsp;it.
